в”Ӯ available. I need to place the patch inside the `SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint` function.                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ My goal is to fix a dominance issue. The SLP vectorizer needs to place new instructions at a point that is dominated by all of its operands. The `getInsertPoint` function calculates    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ this point. My fix involves refining the choice of the insertion block (`Block`) by ensuring it's dominated by the blocks of all scalar operands (`VL`).                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ I've had trouble locating the exact line number for `getInsertPoint`. I will now search for a unique string within that function to find the correct location. A good candidate is the   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ initialization of the `Block` variable: `BasicBlock *Block = getSameBlock(VL);`. After this line and the subsequent null check, the `Block` variable is established. This is the perfect в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ place to insert my logic to further constrain `Block` based on operand dominance.                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ I will search for the line `if (!Block)` which immediately follows the initialization of `Block`, and insert my code after the `if` block. This seems like a robust way to locate the    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ correct position without relying on exact line numbers which have proven unreliable.                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ sed -i '/^    if (!Block) {$/,/^\    }$/a\                                                                                                                                               в”Ӯ
