в”Ӯ THOUGHT                                                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The user wants me to fix a crash in the LLVM SLP vectorizer. The crash is a verifier error, `Instruction does not dominate all uses!`, which indicates that the vectorizer is generating в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ invalid LLVM IR. My previous attempts to patch `SLPVectorizer.cpp` failed due to compilation errors, as I was inserting code into the wrong scope.                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The root cause of the crash is that `SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint` incorrectly determines the insertion point for new vector instructions when operands come from different basic       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ blocks. The chosen insertion point is not always dominated by the definitions of all operands, leading to an invalid IR.                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ To fix this, I will modify `getInsertPoint`. The correct approach is to find a basic block that is a common dominator for the parent blocks of all instruction operands in the           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ vectorization group (`VL`). Then, this block must also be a common dominator for the blocks of all users of these operands.                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ My patch will do the following:                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1.  Initialize `Block` to null.                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2.  Iterate through all values in `VL`. If a value is an instruction, update `Block` to be the nearest common dominator of the current `Block` and the instruction's parent block. This  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ensures the resulting `Block` is dominated by all operand definitions.                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3.  Then, iterate through all users of the values in `VL`. Update `Block` to be the nearest common dominator of the current `Block` and each user's parent block. This ensures the       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ `Block` also dominates all uses.                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4.  Finally, the insertion point `IP` is set to the terminator of this correctly computed `Block`. This is a safe insertion point.                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ This logic correctly computes a valid insertion block and point, resolving the dominance issue. I will use `sed` to replace the existing, flawed implementation of `getInsertPoint` with в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ this new, correct logic.                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ sed -i '/^Instruction \*SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value \*> VL) const {$/,/^}$/c\                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Instruction *SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value *> VL) const {\                                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   BasicBlock *Block = nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     auto *I = dyn_cast<Instruction>(V);\                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     if (!I)\                                                                                                                                                                             в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       continue;\                                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       Block = I->getParent();\                                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     else\                                                                                                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, I->getParent());\                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     return nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     for (User *U : V->users()) {\                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       auto *I = cast<Instruction>(U);\                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, I->getParent());\                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     }\                                                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   return Block->getTerminator();\                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      в”Ӯ
