в”Ӯ The user wants me to fix a crash in the LLVM SLP vectorizer. The crash is a verifier error, `Instruction does not dominate all uses!`, which indicates that the vectorizer is generating в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ invalid LLVM IR. This happens when vectorizing scalars from different basic blocks, as the insertion point for the new vector instructions is not always dominated by the definitions of в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ all scalar operands.                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ My previous attempts to patch the `SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint` function failed due to compilation errors. The `sed` commands were not precise enough and modified the wrong parts of  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ the file.                                                                                                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The core of the problem is that `getInsertPoint` does not correctly determine the insertion block when operands come from different basic blocks. The existing logic only computes a     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ common dominator for the operands if they are all in different blocks. If some are in the same block, it uses that block, which might not be dominated by the other operands.            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ To fix this, I will modify `getInsertPoint` to *always* compute the common dominator of all scalar operand blocks. This ensures the resulting insertion block is dominated by all        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ operand definitions. The logic will be:                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1.  Initialize `Block` to `nullptr`.                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2.  Iterate through all scalar values (`VL`). If a value is an instruction, update `Block` to be the nearest common dominator of the current `Block` and the instruction's parent block. в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3.  After finding the common dominator for operands, do the same for all *users* of the operands to ensure the insertion point also dominates all uses.                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4.  Finally, find the earliest possible insertion point within this block that is after all operands and before all users. A simple and safe choice is the block's terminator.           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ I will use a `sed` command to replace the entire body of the `getInsertPoint` function with this new, correct implementation. This avoids the scoping issues from previous attempts.     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ sed -i '/^Instruction \*SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value \*> VL) const {$/,/^}$/c\                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Instruction *SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value *> VL) const {\                                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   BasicBlock *Block = nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     if (auto *I = dyn_cast<Instruction>(V)) {\                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = I->getParent();\                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       else\                                                                                                                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, I->getParent());\                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     } else if (auto *A = dyn_cast<Argument>(V)) {\                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = &A->getParent()->getEntryBlock();\                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       else\                                                                                                                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, &A->getParent()->getEntryBlock());\                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     }\                                                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     return nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Instruction *IP = Block->getTerminator();\                                                                                                                                             в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     for (User *U : V->users()) {\                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       auto *I = cast<Instruction>(U);\                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       if (I->getParent() == Block) {\                                                                                                                                                    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         if (IP->comesBefore(I))\                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ           IP = I;\                                                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       } else {\                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, I->getParent());\                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       }\                                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     }\                                                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   if (IP->getParent() != Block)\                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     return Block->getTerminator();\                                                                                                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   return IP;\                                                                                                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      в”Ӯ
