в”Ӯ The core of the problem is that `getInsertPoint` does not correctly determine the insertion block when operands come from different basic blocks. The existing logic is flawed.          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ To fix this, I will replace the entire body of `getInsertPoint` with a correct implementation. The logic is as follows:                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1.  Find a `Block` that is the nearest common dominator of the parent blocks of all scalar `Instruction` operands in the vectorization list `VL`. This ensures the insertion point will  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ be dominated by all operand definitions.                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2.  If there are no instruction operands (e.g., only arguments or constants), find the entry block of the function.                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3.  If no suitable block can be found, return `nullptr`.                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4.  The safest insertion point within this common dominator `Block` is its terminator instruction. This guarantees that the new vector instructions are placed after all scalar operands в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ within that block have been defined and before control flow leaves the block.                                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ This approach is simple and robust. It guarantees that any new instruction inserted at this point will have all its scalar operands available (in terms of dominance), thus fixing the   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ verifier error. I will use a `sed` command to replace the entire body of the `getInsertPoint` function with this new, correct implementation. This avoids the scoping issues from        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ previous attempts.                                                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ sed -i '/^Instruction \*SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value \*> VL) const {$/,/^}$/c\                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Instruction *SLPVectorizer::getInsertPoint(ArrayRef<Value *> VL) const {\                                                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   BasicBlock *Block = nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     if (auto *I = dyn_cast<Instruction>(V)) {\                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = I->getParent();\                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       else\                                                                                                                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = DT.findNearestCommonDominator(Block, I->getParent());\                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     }\                                                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   if (!Block) {\                                                                                                                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     for (Value *V : VL) {\                                                                                                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       if (auto *A = dyn_cast<Argument>(V)) {\                                                                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         Block = &A->getParent()->getEntryBlock();\                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ         break;\                                                                                                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ       }\                                                                                                                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     }\                                                                                                                                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }\                                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   if (!Block)\                                                                                                                                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     return nullptr;\                                                                                                                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ \                                                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   return Block->getTerminator();\                                                                                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp                                                                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      в”Ӯ
